TestCase_GC_000120_Read_100k ( )
Trusted Applications dependencies:
63079a66f454511d9221a732faeb1c6a
Focus:
File 100k read benchmark using secure timer. timer measure read operation only (OPEN and CLOSE excluded from the loop)
Test Steps:
1) create persistent object with initial data 2) Open persistent object 3) Start Secure Timer 4) Read object 5) Stop Secure Timer 6) Close the persistent object 7) Accumulate elapsed time from timer 8) Repeat file.nbRead times
Manual Execution:
No
Trustonic Test Suite Testcase:
No
Final Device Testcase:
No
Extensive Testcase:
No
Basic Testcase:
No
Quick Testcase:
No
Minimum Product Version required for this testcase:
